document_data.caption: A map showing Stench Alley and surroundings in the Field Ward of Waterdeep.
document_data.name: Stench Alley
document_data.mainbody: '''Stench Alley''' was a small alley that was located in the city of [[Waterdeep]] during the 15{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: Stench Alley was located in the eastern section of Waterdeep's [[Waterdeep/Field Ward|Field Ward]]. It branched south off of [[Chop Street]], branching several more times to connect with [[Logan's Walk]] and [[Tanner Alley]].
